{"tid":2168048,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"做個時髦人 - 李純恩","createTime":"2020-08-21T13:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T13:13:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b46f7b563900442ed448ffaf9e6cf1b797b49fec","tid":2168048,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:13:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/D5NX3BLDVJF27BPUKW76PFI6BQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FD5NX3BLDVJF27BPUKW76PFI6BQ%2F&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThm%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=f3e64d39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FD5NX3BLDVJF27BPUKW76PFI6BQ%2F&h=5c56504f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/D5NX3BLDVJF27BPUKW76PFI6BQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n做個時髦人 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_c2gqciYsMYkrDCeK3HO1D1HoGg=/960x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BYPTFRBYABB57PKMKM47KREKVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_c2gqciYsMYkrDCeK3HO1D1HoGg%3D%2F960x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBYPTFRBYABB57PKMKM47KREKVY.jpg&h=29c08f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了跟國際反種族主義的先進意識接軌，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我很得意自己革命覺悟高了，並且想出「避黑之法」。以後，逢「黑」就說「不白」，「幕後黑手」就是「幕後不白手」，「黑社會」就是「不白社會」，「黑黑實實」就是「不白不白實實」，「漫長的黑夜」就是「漫長的不白夜」，「黑洞」就是「不白洞」，如果連「黑人」都令人覺得有貶意，那就叫「不白人」，諸如此類，凡是有貶黑意思的，都說「不白」，一招見效，可保政治正確，跟浩浩蕩蕩的世界潮流接軌，順之而昌，做個時髦人。<br />\n<br />\n當然，「黑」字也不要徹底捨棄，可以專門用在那些褒獎「白」的名詞中，比如「黑手興家」、「清黑做人」、「一清二黑」、「一黑遮三醜」（只要黑得深，十醜都可遮），「美黑」、「浪裏黑條」、「藍天黑雲」、「真相大黑」，&mdash;&mdash;諸如此類，好事都黑，一招見效，可保政治正確，做個明黑時髦人。<br />\n<br />\n如此這般，連色盲都不是病了，世界真正公平了。"}]}